dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.diagnosticextract.dcm

Interface IDiagnosticAccessPermission

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDiagnosticCommonElement, IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable

    public interface IDiagnosticAccessPermission
extends IEntity, IDiagnosticCommonElement
    IDiagnosticAccessPermission: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This represents the specification of whether a given service can be accessed according to the existence of meta-classes referenced by a particular DiagnosticAccessPermission. In other words, this meta-class acts as a mapping element between several (otherwise unrelated) pieces of information that are put into context for the purpose of checking for access rights.
